msgid "Play a simple tone."
msgstr "播放简单的音调声音。"

#: ../../source/hardware/speaker.rst:299 2e0423df9d174836ad017930a289a216
msgid "``frequency`` is the frequency of the tone in Hz."
msgstr "``frequency`` 是音调的频率，单位是 Hz。"

#: ../../source/hardware/speaker.rst:300 81e186e67008432d86213cef078b8a09
msgid "``duration`` is the duration of the tone in milliseconds."
msgstr "``duration`` 是音调的持续时间，单位是毫秒。"

#: ../../source/hardware/speaker.rst:301 ../../source/hardware/speaker.rst:319
#: ../../source/hardware/speaker.rst:335 ../../source/hardware/speaker.rst:350
#: 23a6b035ce3c41f98ca14ebf29068771 3aa9a7281fd74ac0bef42a63b0cf6ce1
#: 5039584fb7594872b6ac78997b20406b f55e6c7f1bb348c98c254b9366da7a77
msgid ""
"``channel`` is the channel to play, ranging from 0 to 7. By default, it "
"is -1, which means using an available channel."
msgstr "``channel`` 是播放的通道，范围是 0 ~ 7 ，默认填 -1 ，使用可用的通道播放。"

#: ../../source/hardware/speaker.rst:302 ../../source/hardware/speaker.rst:320
#: ../../source/hardware/speaker.rst:336 ../../source/hardware/speaker.rst:351
#: 539a4a5cd8a2418c8590a346ec137acc 68286e4e89564b9b9774a97287fed2ab
#: d13b0c5078694186875381dd656242bf dccb7a18b0eb4c3891a474c23a680029
msgid ""
"``stop_current_sound`` controls whether to wait for the previous audio "
"playback to finish. If True, start the new output without waiting for the"
" current output to finish."
msgstr "``stop_current_sound`` 用于控制是否等待之前的音频播放完成，为 True 时，无需等待当前输出完成即可开始新的输出。"

